{"tid":2167782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見到大律師公會是日的聲明,我又係時間追債","createTime":"2020-08-21T10:27:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T03:22:44.000Z","uid":26770,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"91d10a590534e32e86224082864d3cf53f305128","tid":2167782,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:27:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkba.org/sites/default/files/20200821%20-%20HKBA%20Statement%20on%20Criticisms%20of%20Factual%20Findings%20of%20Judicial%20Officers%20%28C%29.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkba.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F20200821%2520-%2520HKBA%2520Statement%2520on%2520Criticisms%2520of%2520Factual%2520Findings%2520of%2520Judicial%2520Officers%2520%2528C%2529.pdf&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliuw9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=fb2be0c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkba.org/sites/default/files/20200821%20-%20HKBA%20Statement%20on%20Criticisms%20of%20Factual%20Findings%20of%20Judicial%20Officers%20%28C%29.pdf</a><br />\n<strong>8月21日出聲明講任何人屌法官公會都會護航<br />\n姐係日日公會都正常營業中</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">大律師公會幾時回應</span><br />\n<br />\n1) 點解警員口供完全矛盾<br />\n香港法庭(陳慧敏,張潔宜)照判示威者坐監未<br />\n<br />\n2)法援署署長鄺寶昌指示阻礙暴動案被告申請法援<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2166932\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2166932</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">3)的士司機鄭國泉開車撞異見者,係文明國家係恐怖份子<br />\ndoj唔告,助理刑事檢控專員蕭啟業更加破壞許議員的私人檢控<br />\n大律師公會的立場是什麼</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2164999/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2164999/</a>"},{"pid":"2f19d78a86b01e8ebc6864b45d6c4c1184d25070","tid":2167782,"uid":287422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:27:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091ab34f9f4a1fb57b40003953dc00c550d3808c","tid":2167782,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7884bde05c78fdd9403bfb52a6cd2df7a4d97113","tid":2167782,"uid":26770,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:34:56.000Z","msg":"出聲明維護法院就叻<br />\n問你野就扮盲唔答<br />\n<br />\n大家睇暴動案刑期係幾長<br />\n<br />\n<strong>法援署署長鄺寶昌指示阻礙暴動案被告申請法援係令到班政治異見者得唔到合適的法律代表</strong><br />\n<br />\n做到呢個地步大律師公會班人仲日日寫文稱讚香港法官專業,咩9野有法治<br />\n<br />\n根本大陸屍公會就係司法迫害的共犯"},{"pid":"99ba3c7f61d3821ba2266c2da065221123d7acc1","tid":2167782,"uid":108462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:37:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e04b0844b7f4b191ede6d360bf581861fe15c44","tid":2167782,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T11:33:28.000Z","msg":"維穩會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd6228713646377c1add6ef2836c2f4e927f21b6","tid":2167782,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T11:38:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d017e2e648be50cebcf8847b0d18887032e0c76","tid":2167782,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T11:48:53.000Z","msg":"梁定邦當日以監警會主席身份支持警魔隱瞞身份<br />\n導致警魔隱瞞身份行去<strong>私刑及輪姦女性</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2025287/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2025287/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>而梁定邦就係大律師公會的大大佬<br />\n(因為香港資深大律師人數好少)</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hk-lawyer.org/tc/content/%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E7%9B%A3%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-%E6%A2%81%E5%AE%9A%E9%82%A6-%E8%B3%87%E6%B7%B1%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%EF%BC%8Cjp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk-lawyer.org%2Ftc%2Fcontent%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E7%259B%25A3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%25AE%259A%25E9%2582%25A6-%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25EF%25BC%258Cjp&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliuw9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=13d189b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk-lawyer.org/tc/content/%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E7%9B%A3%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-%E6%A2%81%E5%AE%9A%E9%82%A6-%E8%B3%87%E6%B7%B1%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%EF%BC%8Cjp</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">大律師公會有責任就核心會員支持強姦婦女表態</span></span>"},{"pid":"87e8f19f0045f1cbf922c78151546df583445d5c","tid":2167782,"uid":40520,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T11:52:10.000Z","msg":"泛登仔:大律師公會好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554e65f5299b606f66dde17c57496d128122f3b9","tid":2167782,"uid":40520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T11:53:38.000Z","msg":"泛登仔:戴啟思幫緊手足打官司 好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7da6beb33e3b1bc49429e16